{"tid":903501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[真 調理農務系] 推首個農業相關學科　浸大首批收15人料2020畢業","createTime":"2018-11-15T14:58:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T20:17:57.000Z","uid":66324,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"76d18775ea9fe15577a0083375580d9dd956a005","tid":903501,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:58:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%8E%A8%E9%A6%96%E5%80%8B%E8%BE%B2%E6%A5%AD%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E5%AD%B8%E7%A7%91%E3%80%80%E6%B5%B8%E5%A4%A7%E9%A6%96%E6%89%B9%E6%94%B615%E4%BA%BA%E6%96%992020%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD-149885\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%258E%25A8%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%2580%258B%25E8%25BE%25B2%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%259B%25B8%25E9%2597%259C%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%25A7%2591%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%25B5%25B8%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%2589%25B9%25E6%2594%25B615%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2596%25992020%25E7%2595%25A2%25E6%25A5%25AD-149885&d=nn2eebiMG5RM5StdFdZfXARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=01d786ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%8E%A8%E9%A6%96%E5%80%8B%E8%BE%B2%E6%A5%AD%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E5%AD%B8%E7%A7%91%E3%80%80%E6%B5%B8%E5%A4%A7%E9%A6%96%E6%89%B9%E6%94%B615%E4%BA%BA%E6%96%992020%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD-149885</a><br />\n<br />\n政府擬於新界上水古洞南設立農業園。浸會大學將於明年9月推本港首個農業相關學科「生物資源與農業科學理學士(榮譽)」，望培育港產農業人材及發展可持續農業。<br />\n<br />\n學科除著重農業科學，亦注重教授生物資源及農業市場管理。浸大生物系系主任黃煥忠(圖中)表示，農業雖只佔本地GDP不足1%，但可持續農業能為香港帶來新經濟機遇，以支持經濟產業多元化，提升本地農業的自給率。<br />\n<br />\n浸大生物資源與農業研究所主席黃志光(圖右)表示，農業正邁向科學化、企業化及環保化，不再是以鋤頭或拖拉機耕作。他又認為休閒農業在本港具很大發展空間，可透過耕作教育下一代食物從何而來，從中學懂珍惜。<br />\n<br />\n黃煥忠指有意入讀的學生須先入讀理學士，至2年級可選擇新課程作主修，現階段暫定招收15人，若反應熱烈或會增至最多30人，首批學生料2020年開始修讀。"},{"pid":"8012a12baf8262455296eb4e38dad53202f71055","tid":903501,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T18:36:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ffaf5db1dedc20df3fc83edaf227c516c60aa2a","tid":903501,"uid":29702,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T18:37:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c287a959ed95fc8c718f9ed836ef57129e391b7","tid":903501,"uid":156363,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T20:08:33.000Z","msg":"侵大就黎變I大喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a77021ed9920cd6dcf617301f201dac82947099","tid":903501,"uid":12370,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4ffaf5db1dedc20df3fc83edaf227c516c60aa2a","tid":903501,"uid":29702,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T18:37:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T20:12:42.000Z","msg":"唔係讀來移民用呢科係香港仲慘過讀哲學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13fd7d1ea179ee0fa16575e351f54e46a866c599","tid":903501,"uid":117200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T20:17:57.000Z","msg":"做農夫都要有個化學工程學位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}